bination with other agents that are potentially hepatotoxic (e.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/45513/', '', 'Lamivudine, Paritaprevir, Glecaprevir, Tenofovir alafenamide, Maraviroc, Amprenavir, Simeprevir, Valaciclovir, Zanamivir, Cabotegravir, Lenacapavir, More', 'Pertuzumab, Cetuximab, Avelumab, Panitumumab, Obinutuzumab, Bevacizumab, Necitumumab, Dostarlimab, Ramucirumab, Atezolizumab, Amivantamab, More', 1767369485);
